  "messages": [
    {
      "id": 1405,
      "from_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "to_id": "human",
      "content": "Spec written to .synapse/tasks/101-plan.md. Summary:\n\n**Problem:** Orchestrator must embed its own agent_id as a literal string in spawn text (fragile). No readiness signal — worker might still be booting when first task arrives.\n\n**Proposed: First-message handshake**\n1. `spawn_agent` returns worker_agent_id (already works today)\n2. Orchestrator sends worker a handshake message containing orchestrator_id\n3. Worker reads it, stores orchestrator_id, sends \"ready\" back\n4. Orchestrator only delegates tasks after receiving \"ready\"\n\n…\n\n[Full report: .synapse/reports/1780926970632-spec-written-to-synapse-tasks-101-plan-m.md]",
      "priority": 5,
      "created_at": 1780926970632,
      "read_at": null,
      "needs_approval": 0,
      "approved_at": null,
      "request_options": null,
      "selected_option": null,
      "task_id": null,
      "type": "finding"
    },
    {
      "id": 1406,
      "from_id": "human",
      "to_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "content": "One more issue: there are different type of files per task, plan, handoff, report, review etc. We don't have rule for them yet. Put into the ORCH md where we scetches a little already",
      "priority": 5,
      "created_at": 1780927064172,
      "read_at": 1780927066547,
      "needs_approval": 0,
      "approved_at": null,
      "request_options": null,
      "selected_option": null,
      "task_id": null,
      "type": "message"
    },
    {
      "id": 1407,
      "from_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "to_id": "human",
      "content": "Added Task Files section to SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md with a table covering all four file types:\n\n| File | Writer | Reader |\n|---|---|---|\n| `<id>-plan.md` | Orchestrator (via subagent) | Worker, before executing |\n| `<id>.md` | Orchestrator (delegate_task handoff) | Worker, as task instructions |\n| `<id>-report.md` | Worker (report_done with report_file:true) | Orchestrator, after DONE |\n| `<id>-review.md` | Code-reviewer worker | Orchestrator, before merge |\n\nAlso updated the Canonical Sequence steps 4–6 to reference the specific file types.\n\nApprove to copy to .synapse/ and commit?",
